{"tid":1054513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"色男大生畢旅裝針孔　偷拍櫻花妹同學洗澡","createTime":"2019-03-10T00:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T04:39:48.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"56df246aec61c8996bfb039f1ebfcf8dae7d35e5","tid":1054513,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T00:19:54.000Z","msg":"大學生一起去畢業旅行，租了一棟別墅成為大家下褟的地點，沒想到其中一名男大生，在浴室偷裝攝影機偷拍女生入浴，被女大生抓包後報警處理。<br />\n據《日刊gendai》報導，在別墅浴室裝攝影機偷拍的22歲明珍敦士，2月20日被兵庫縣警方以違反縣迷惑防止條例逮捕。明珍敦士跟7男、7女同班同學，共15人，租了淡路島海水浴場旁的別墅，作為2天1夜旅行的下褟地點。<br />\n調查人員指出，「該別墅是棟木屋，沒有管理人員，凌晨的時候有兩名女大生要去洗澡，在脫衣服的時候聽到天花板掉下東西的聲音，仔細一看，竟然是有鏡頭的煙霧感應器，於是拿著去跟男生們對質，明珍敦士才坦承犯行」，而除了煙霧感應器有鏡頭外，調查人員發現火災警報器、時鐘、衣架，都藏有偷拍鏡頭。<br />\n對於警方的調查，明珍敦士坦承犯行，「想看女生的裸體」，調查人員表示，目前正在調查攝影機裡面拍了什麼內容，而且可以不被其他人發現，在別墅偷裝攝影機，讓人感覺是慣犯，至於是自己收藏還是上網賣偷拍畫面，有待警方調查。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190310/640_1f67495905db48118d2b9c1014edf989.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190310%2F640_1f67495905db48118d2b9c1014edf989.jpg&h=3a967333&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a31dc9ea41a00b86d767523de703902edebb110","tid":1054513,"uid":55386,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T00:31:56.000Z","msg":"張圖想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2fda0a1af1dcbd9bbcefeacc4e8c5aaa6c22def","tid":1054513,"uid":203543,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T00:35:54.000Z","msg":"估錯國家"},{"pid":"d781fa4eefa334d13fb840688a84130a241fe71a","tid":1054513,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2fda0a1af1dcbd9bbcefeacc4e8c5aaa6c22def","tid":1054513,"uid":203543,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T00:35:54.000Z","msg":"估錯國家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T00:47:54.000Z","msg":"我都估錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed3cdcd2ea2d4ce2f35713676291a6184d46946","tid":1054513,"uid":36238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T00:53:27.000Z","msg":"寫明櫻花妹點會估錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42b5bca3f3539c220fd6d39aa484a636c000166f","tid":1054513,"uid":227262,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:02:27.000Z","msg":"本身廁所會裝煙幕感應器都令人懷疑啦，搏佢沖沖下涼嚮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n識裝肯定係改裝浴室寶然後係排氣口裝鏡頭，睇都睇唔到，仲好合理，唔明條友咁撚蠢點做大學生，仲要跌落黎嗰下柒<br />\n<br />\n利申：無做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0338a3ab5c3ac131ef53a6fa88bb22a5a19373","tid":1054513,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ed3cdcd2ea2d4ce2f35713676291a6184d46946","tid":1054513,"uid":36238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T00:53:27.000Z","msg":"寫明櫻花妹點會估錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:07:19.000Z","msg":"櫻花妹去台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbaf0d3656818eb05cbab99cc30883b28616021f","tid":1054513,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:14:41.000Z","msg":"都一起去旅行都食左啦<br />\n仲要拍"},{"pid":"72445ba52b9ac540479179ced9a7d48ff4e68003","tid":1054513,"uid":39878,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:21:23.000Z","msg":"仲以為個犯叫夏健祺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9d0825cc68b46708c231be50f0dee76b35ec0d","tid":1054513,"uid":49776,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dbaf0d3656818eb05cbab99cc30883b28616021f","tid":1054513,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:14:41.000Z","msg":"都一起去旅行都食左啦<br />\n仲要拍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:42:00.000Z","msg":"8男7女咪淨返佢"},{"pid":"a9662c45f72cf1c94fdf7bcb7ad47c94b3ff62c2","tid":1054513,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s